WEBVTT

32:36.770 --> 32:37.700 line:80%
♪ I pray that our love
will not be like sand ♪

32:37.040 --> 32:39.120 line:80%
I'm telling you
not to fear people's words.

32:37.720 --> 32:40.180 line:80%
♪ Slipping into the sea ♪

32:40.480 --> 32:42.000 line:80%
Spreading rumors and slandering

32:41.510 --> 32:42.450 line:80%
♪ I'd rather use this life ♪

32:42.110 --> 32:43.480 line:80%
costs nothing

32:42.470 --> 32:44.910 line:80%
♪ To guard our love forever ♪

32:43.910 --> 32:45.440 line:80%
but causes great harm,

32:45.480 --> 32:46.830 line:80%
especially to women.

32:45.620 --> 32:49.510 line:80%
♪ Clear and quiet as me ♪
